HEADWORD: Speechifying
<hw>Speech"i*fy`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of making a speech
or speeches.</def> <mark>[Used derisively or humorously.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The dinner and <qex>speechifying</qex> . . . at the opening of the
annual season for the buckhounds.</q> <rj><qau>M. Arnold.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

